c: 46
v: 21
t: "“Ndipo kumbuka za m’bale wa Âdi, (mtumiki Hûd) pamene adachenjeza anthu ake kudziko la milu ya mchenga. Ndithu adaliponso achenjezi iye asadadze ndiponso iye atapita. (Iye adawauza anthu ake): “Musampembedze aliyense koma Allah; ndithu ine ndikukuoperani chilango cha tsiku lalikulu.”"